verses.text_plain: And the second lot came forth to Simeon, even for the tribe of the children of Simeon according to their families: and their inheritance was within the inheritance of the children of Judah.
verses.verse_html: 1And the second lot came forth to Simeon, even for the tribe of the children of Simeon according to their families: and their inheritance was within the inheritance of the children of Judah.

verses.text_plain: And they had in their inheritance Beer–sheba, Sheba, and Moladah,
verses.verse_html: 2And they had in their inheritance Beer–sheba, Sheba, and Moladah,

tokens.text: And they had in their inheritance

verses.text_plain: And Hazar–shual, and Balah, and Azem,
verses.verse_html: 3And Hazar–shual, and Balah, and Azem,

verses.text_plain: And Eltolad, and Bethul, and Hormah,
verses.verse_html: 4And Eltolad, and Bethul, and Hormah,

verses.text_plain: And Ziklag, and Beth–marcaboth, and Hazar–susah,
verses.verse_html: 5And Ziklag, and Beth–marcaboth, and Hazar–susah,

verses.text_plain: And Beth–lebaoth, and Sharuhen; thirteen cities and their villages:
verses.verse_html: 6And Beth–lebaoth, and Sharuhen; thirteen cities and their villages:

verses.text_plain: Ain, Remmon, and Ether, and Ashan; four cities and their villages:
verses.verse_html: 7Ain, Remmon, and Ether, and Ashan; four cities and their villages:

verses.text_plain: And all the villages that were round about these cities to Baalath–beer, Ramath of the south. This is the inheritance of the tribe of the children of Simeon according to their families.
verses.verse_html: 8And all the villages that were round about these cities to Baalath–beer, Ramath of the south. This is the inheritance of the tribe of the children of Simeon according to their families.

verses.text_plain: Out of the portion of the children of Judah was the inheritance of the children of Simeon: for the part of the children of Judah was too much for them: therefore the children of Simeon had their inheritance within the inheritance of them.
verses.verse_html: 9Out of the portion of the children of Judah was the inheritance of the children of Simeon: for the part of the children of Judah was too much for them: therefore the children of Simeon had their inheritance within the inheritance of them.

verses.text_plain: And the third lot came up for the children of Zebulun according to their families: and the border of their inheritance was unto Sarid:
verses.verse_html: 10And the third lot came up for the children of Zebulun according to their families: and the border of their inheritance was unto Sarid:

verses.text_plain: And their border went up toward the sea, and Maralah, and reached to Dabbasheth, and reached to the river that is before Jokneam;
verses.verse_html: 11And their border went up toward the sea, and Maralah, and reached to Dabbasheth, and reached to the river that is before Jokneam;

verses.text_plain: And turned from Sarid eastward toward the sunrising unto the border of Chisloth–tabor, and then goeth out to Daberath, and goeth up to Japhia,
verses.verse_html: 12And turned from Sarid eastward toward the sunrising unto the border of Chisloth–tabor, and then goeth out to Daberath, and goeth up to Japhia,

verses.text_plain: And from thence passeth on along on the east to Gittah–hepher, to Ittah–kazin, and goeth out to Remmon–methoar to Neah;
verses.verse_html:
13And from thence passeth on along on the east to Gittah–hepher, to Ittah–kazin, and goeth out to Remmon–methoar to Neah; ▼
▼ methoar: or, which is drawn

tokens.text: And from thence passeth on along

footnotes.body_html: ▼ methoar: or, which is drawn

verses.text_plain: And the border compasseth it on the north side to Hannathon: and the outgoings thereof are in the valley of Jiphthah–el:
verses.verse_html: 14And the border compasseth it on the north side to Hannathon: and the outgoings thereof are in the valley of Jiphthah–el:

verses.text_plain: And Kattath, and Nahallal, and Shimron, and Idalah, and Beth–lehem: twelve cities with their villages.
verses.verse_html: 15And Kattath, and Nahallal, and Shimron, and Idalah, and Beth–lehem: twelve cities with their villages.

verses.text_plain: This is the inheritance of the children of Zebulun according to their families, these cities with their villages.
verses.verse_html: 16This is the inheritance of the children of Zebulun according to their families, these cities with their villages.

verses.text_plain: And the fourth lot came out to Issachar, for the children of Issachar according to their families.
verses.verse_html: 17And the fourth lot came out to Issachar, for the children of Issachar according to their families.

verses.text_plain: And their border was toward Jezreel, and Chesulloth, and Shunem,
verses.verse_html: 18And their border was toward Jezreel, and Chesulloth, and Shunem,

verses.text_plain: And Hapharaim, and Shion, and Anaharath,
verses.verse_html: 19And Hapharaim, and Shion, and Anaharath,

verses.text_plain: And Rabbith, and Kishion, and Abez,
verses.verse_html: 20And Rabbith, and Kishion, and Abez,

verses.text_plain: And Remeth, and En–gannim, and En–haddah, and Beth–pazzez;
verses.verse_html: 21And Remeth, and En–gannim, and En–haddah, and Beth–pazzez;

verses.text_plain: And the coast reacheth to Tabor, and Shahazimah, and Beth–shemesh; and the outgoings of their border were at Jordan: sixteen cities with their villages.
verses.verse_html: 22And the coast reacheth to Tabor, and Shahazimah, and Beth–shemesh; and the outgoings of their border were at Jordan: sixteen cities with their villages.

verses.text_plain: This is the inheritance of the tribe of the children of Issachar according to their families, the cities and their villages.
verses.verse_html: 23This is the inheritance of the tribe of the children of Issachar according to their families, the cities and their villages.

verses.text_plain: And the fifth lot came out for the tribe of the children of Asher according to their families.
verses.verse_html: 24And the fifth lot came out for the tribe of the children of Asher according to their families.

verses.text_plain: And their border was Helkath, and Hali, and Beten, and Achshaph,
verses.verse_html: 25And their border was Helkath, and Hali, and Beten, and Achshaph,

verses.text_plain: And Alammelech, and Amad, and Misheal; and reacheth to Carmel westward, and to Shihor–libnath;
verses.verse_html: 26And Alammelech, and Amad, and Misheal; and reacheth to Carmel westward, and to Shihor–libnath;

verses.text_plain: And turneth toward the sunrising to Beth–dagon, and reacheth to Zebulun, and to the valley of Jiphthah–el toward the north side of Beth–emek, and Neiel, and goeth out to Cabul on the left hand,
verses.verse_html: 27And turneth toward the sunrising to Beth–dagon, and reacheth to Zebulun, and to the valley of Jiphthah–el toward the north side of Beth–emek, and Neiel, and goeth out to Cabul on the left hand,

verses.text_plain: And Hebron, and Rehob, and Hammon, and Kanah, even unto great Zidon;
verses.verse_html: 28And Hebron, and Rehob, and Hammon, and Kanah, even unto great Zidon;

verses.text_plain: And then the coast turneth to Ramah, and to the strong city Tyre; and the coast turneth to Hosah; and the outgoings thereof are at the sea from the coast to Achzib:
verses.verse_html:
29And then the coast turneth to Ramah, and to the strong city Tyre; and the coast turneth to Hosah; and the outgoings thereof are at the sea from the coast to Achzib: ▼
▼ Tyre: Heb. Tzor

verses.text_plain: Ummah also, and Aphek, and Rehob: twenty and two cities with their villages.
verses.verse_html: 30Ummah also, and Aphek, and Rehob: twenty and two cities with their villages.

verses.text_plain: This is the inheritance of the tribe of the children of Asher according to their families, these cities with their villages.
verses.verse_html: 31This is the inheritance of the tribe of the children of Asher according to their families, these cities with their villages.

verses.text_plain: The sixth lot came out to the children of Naphtali, even for the children of Naphtali according to their families.
verses.verse_html: 32The sixth lot came out to the children of Naphtali, even for the children of Naphtali according to their families.

verses.text_plain: And their coast was from Heleph, from Allon to Zaanannim, and Adami, Nekeb, and Jabneel, unto Lakum; and the outgoings thereof were at Jordan:
verses.verse_html: 33And their coast was from Heleph, from Allon to Zaanannim, and Adami, Nekeb, and Jabneel, unto Lakum; and the outgoings thereof were at Jordan:

verses.text_plain: And then the coast turneth westward to Aznoth–tabor, and goeth out from thence to Hukkok, and reacheth to Zebulun on the south side, and reacheth to Asher on the west side, and to Judah upon Jordan toward the sunrising.
verses.verse_html: 34And then the coast turneth westward to Aznoth–tabor, and goeth out from thence to Hukkok, and reacheth to Zebulun on the south side, and reacheth to Asher on the west side, and to Judah upon Jordan toward the sunrising.

verses.text_plain: And the fenced cities are Ziddim, Zer, and Hammath, Rakkath, and Chinnereth,
verses.verse_html: 35And the fenced cities are Ziddim, Zer, and Hammath, Rakkath, and Chinnereth,

verses.text_plain: And Adamah, and Ramah, and Hazor,
verses.verse_html: 36And Adamah, and Ramah, and Hazor,

verses.text_plain: And Kedesh, and Edrei, and En–hazor,
verses.verse_html: 37And Kedesh, and Edrei, and En–hazor,

verses.text_plain: And Iron, and Migdal–el, Horem, and Beth–anath, and Beth–shemesh; nineteen cities with their villages.
verses.verse_html: 38And Iron, and Migdal–el, Horem, and Beth–anath, and Beth–shemesh; nineteen cities with their villages.

verses.text_plain: This is the inheritance of the tribe of the children of Naphtali according to their families, the cities and their villages.
verses.verse_html: 39This is the inheritance of the tribe of the children of Naphtali according to their families, the cities and their villages.

verses.text_plain: And the seventh lot came out for the tribe of the children of Dan according to their families.
verses.verse_html: 40And the seventh lot came out for the tribe of the children of Dan according to their families.

verses.text_plain: And the coast of their inheritance was Zorah, and Eshtaol, and Ir–shemesh,
verses.verse_html: 41And the coast of their inheritance was Zorah, and Eshtaol, and Ir–shemesh,

verses.text_plain: And Shaalabbin, and Ajalon, and Jethlah,
verses.verse_html: 42And Shaalabbin, and Ajalon, and Jethlah,

verses.text_plain: And Elon, and Thimnathah, and Ekron,
verses.verse_html: 43And Elon, and Thimnathah, and Ekron,

verses.text_plain: And Eltekeh, and Gibbethon, and Baalath,
verses.verse_html: 44And Eltekeh, and Gibbethon, and Baalath,

verses.text_plain: And Jehud, and Bene–berak, and Gath–rimmon,
verses.verse_html: 45And Jehud, and Bene–berak, and Gath–rimmon,

verses.text_plain: And Me–jarkon, and Rakkon, with the border before Japho.
verses.verse_html:
46And Me–jarkon, and Rakkon, with the border before Japho. ▼
▼ before: or, over against
 , ▼
▼ Japho: or, Joppa

footnotes.body_html: ▼ before: or, over against

verses.text_plain: And the coast of the children of Dan went out too little for them: therefore the children of Dan went up to fight against Leshem, and took it, and smote it with the edge of the sword, and possessed it, and dwelt therein, and called Leshem, Dan, after the name of Dan their father.
verses.verse_html: 47And the coast of the children of Dan went out too little for them: therefore the children of Dan went up to fight against Leshem, and took it, and smote it with the edge of the sword, and possessed it, and dwelt therein, and called Leshem, Dan, after the name of Dan their father.

verses.text_plain: This is the inheritance of the tribe of the children of Dan according to their families, these cities with their villages.
verses.verse_html: 48This is the inheritance of the tribe of the children of Dan according to their families, these cities with their villages.

verses.text_plain: When they had made an end of dividing the land for inheritance by their coasts, the children of Israel gave an inheritance to Joshua the son of Nun among them:
verses.verse_html: 49When they had made an end of dividing the land for inheritance by their coasts, the children of Israel gave an inheritance to Joshua the son of Nun among them:

tokens.text: When they had made an end

verses.text_plain: According to the word of the Lord they gave him the city which he asked, even Timnath–serah in mount Ephraim: and he built the city, and dwelt therein.
verses.verse_html: 50According to the word of the Lord they gave him the city which he asked, even Timnath–serah in mount Ephraim: and he built the city, and dwelt therein.

verses.text_plain: These are the inheritances, which Eleazar the priest, and Joshua the son of Nun, and the heads of the fathers of the tribes of the children of Israel, divided for an inheritance by lot in Shiloh before the Lord, at the door of the tabernacle of the congregation. So they made an end of dividing the country.
verses.verse_html: 51These are the inheritances, which Eleazar the priest, and Joshua the son of Nun, and the heads of the fathers of the tribes of the children of Israel, divided for an inheritance by lot in Shiloh before the Lord, at the door of the tabernacle of the congregation. So they made an end of dividing the country.
